---
<section class="reveal bg-[#1D2F40] pt-[3em] pb-0 px-[1em] transition-all duration-300">
  <div class="max-w-[1340px] w-full mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="p-[1em]">
        <h2 class="font-nav text-[14.4px] font-semibold leading-[1] tracking-[2px] text-[#B9CDE0] uppercase mb-[14px]">FAQ</h2>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-[36px] md:text-[52.8px] font-semibold leading-[1.2] text-[#F4F4F4]">Most Favorite Question</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="p-[1em] flex items-end">
        <p class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-[#D9D9D9]">
          Feel free to connect with us directly for a personalized experience. If you prefer to chat, you can reach us on Skype using our ID: christina619116. We're here to answer any further questions, discuss your specific requirements, or provide any additional information you may need. We look forward to chatting with you and assisting you in any way we can.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-[#1D2F40] pb-[3em] px-[1em]">
  <div class="max-w-[1340px] w-full mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-[20px] p-[1em]">
      <div class="space-y-[20px]">
        <details class="group [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-[20px] py-[18px] bg-transparent border border-[#F4F4F4] rounded-[5px] font-heading text-[1.3rem] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#F4F4F4] group-open:border-[#A6587C]">
            What is the minimum order quantity (MOQ) for custom sportswear?
            <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 text-[#A6587C] group-open:text-[#F4F4F4] ml-2 flex-shrink-0">
              <svg fill="none" height="17" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="17"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-[20px] pt-[18px] pb-[5px] text-[#D9D9D9] font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5]">
            <p>Our MOQ for custom sportswear is flexible and can be tailored to your specific needs. We offer low MOQ options to accommodate both small startups and established brands.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-[20px] py-[18px] bg-transparent border border-[#F4F4F4] rounded-[5px] font-heading text-[1.3rem] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#F4F4F4] group-open:border-[#A6587C]">
            Can I request custom designs for my sportswear?
            <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 text-[#A6587C] group-open:text-[#F4F4F4] ml-2 flex-shrink-0">
              <svg fill="none" height="17" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="17"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-[20px] pt-[18px] pb-[5px] text-[#D9D9D9] font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5]">
            <p>Absolutely! We specialize in custom designs. Our experienced designers will work closely with you to create unique and personalized sportswear that aligns with your brand identity and vision.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-[20px] py-[18px] bg-transparent border border-[#F4F4F4] rounded-[5px] font-heading text-[1.3rem] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#F4F4F4] group-open:border-[#A6587C]">
            What is the turnaround time for producing custom sportswear?
            <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 text-[#A6587C] group-open:text-[#F4F4F4] ml-2 flex-shrink-0">
              <svg fill="none" height="17" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="17"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-[20px] pt-[18px] pb-[5px] text-[#D9D9D9] font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5]">
            <p>The turnaround time depends on the complexity and quantity of your order. However, we prioritize efficiency and timely delivery. Our team will provide you with a clear timeline and strive to meet your deadlines.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-[20px]">
        <details class="group [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-[20px] py-[18px] bg-transparent border border-[#F4F4F4] rounded-[5px] font-heading text-[1.3rem] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#F4F4F4] group-open:border-[#A6587C]">
            Do you use high-quality materials for your sportswear?
            <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 text-[#A6587C] group-open:text-[#F4F4F4] ml-2 flex-shrink-0">
              <svg fill="none" height="17" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="17"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-[20px] pt-[18px] pb-[5px] text-[#D9D9D9] font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5]">
            <p>Yes, we are committed to using only high-quality materials for our sportswear. We understand the importance of durability and comfort, and our materials are carefully selected to ensure the best performance and longevity.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-[20px] py-[18px] bg-transparent border border-[#F4F4F4] rounded-[5px] font-heading text-[1.3rem] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#F4F4F4] group-open:border-[#A6587C]">
            Can I get samples of the sportswear before placing a larger order?
            <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 text-[#A6587C] group-open:text-[#F4F4F4] ml-2 flex-shrink-0">
              <svg fill="none" height="17" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="17"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-[20px] pt-[18px] pb-[5px] text-[#D9D9D9] font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5]">
            <p>Yes, we offer sample orders for you to evaluate the quality, fit, and design of our sportswear. Contact our team, and we will guide you through the sample ordering process.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="group [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
          <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer px-[20px] py-[18px] bg-transparent border border-[#F4F4F4] rounded-[5px] font-heading text-[1.3rem] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#F4F4F4] group-open:border-[#A6587C]">
            Do you ship internationally?
            <span class="transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 text-[#A6587C] group-open:text-[#F4F4F4] ml-2 flex-shrink-0">
              <svg fill="none" height="17" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="17"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-[20px] pt-[18px] pb-[5px] text-[#D9D9D9] font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5]">
            <p>Yes, we ship our sportswear internationally. Wherever you are located, we can deliver your orders to your desired destination using reliable shipping methods.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

